aglqWhj6mUM-i5BrfSt3eEVi8qOacZVVm0pmP33b5lvcCjC85koHHtk_Do43Lyy8p9D7bXevfXzEtfuk1GEo6iWCuU8_jH3HTXpJXMuAKKAJ_CIkkJIkWtJnv0LvhcItl2w4b_0OgzEvhM/yF-5ecVD-XXWiBUTw7K-S7N_M4Cin50M/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;听《创始人：鲍勃·李被杀》&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;必读&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;Gian Volpicelli 在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/_1bKrO2RmNgG1vbfzbjrXPOco3apraJY0sIt1vsMHLbHX_WKP8k2iLE1thNAD4_NdDZaCERnS_hNGAND9xfGmJo5wDP7hhD-laKTycYLypoYI__2qMlCWcQ7osnNHh7Wr2yWQ7JQAzd9_yhIMzXt862gr-mCrhP-WHzOtjJDSOmEH9ZZUHHqY20DHTDi2CrtTqplZ8eK1hsrjg_5IzpkLh64cHO1SFtQ0pvrqA15pH9WuHrGDOmxE31zLrAdYW4f1djYs7QbiZZXJwF1lLdZGB4Xz76p48bxM_w-IkPdEExQkwnFvGet-K0NN9_7A0Yx-oGEtQlwbQ/wl_tSGI2aeXoNDx0A4mJPc5-IpXYChf8/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="芯片工人向三星、SK海力士施压，要求分享利润"&gt;今天的《Tech In Depth》&lt;/a&gt;中报道称，欧盟政策制定者一直处于数字监管短路的痛苦之中。欧盟经常被描述为过于急于调查科技巨头，但在四家科技公司表示将扫描欧洲人的私人通讯中是否存在儿童性虐待材料（CSAM）后，欧盟却耸了耸肩，尽管法律不允许这样做。隐私团体对缺乏行动表示抗议。沃尔皮切利写道，这场辩论围绕着两个核心价值观：保护网络隐私和保护儿童免受网络掠夺者的侵害。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8n03tPbI9iTQyi6Mmmt6q7eQENrc7lBinm_m6pZb8vxGrqm-9UW_bT0OZ-fV1dMaQtAU2Rh__vE8mqUECjw5PmJDDCfWujDMab4VeE0cerHeDr8wSnvFzk4i23TYTjXvEQQHN1leE8ML8GHL7ZVS21LEw5JN2zaIJnWeAIeQ0KIySrQU7_iYDg-j4ZbMjBuK2JzOga_F9GDu8UKXurGo6JISRx4EqeTs-ynpTlcYCCJrca5aIraGcJ6AZo4Da9k2nWg_e0WYg_i0OyoAz6s5602L1i7AGdDBZFY1G0WfN1Hp4wbJje_o6ISXlsAfA0IAEozUy1VD0j0/XWRV30RQ8JMJtiP3PK15CNahtQoRsD4O/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title